{"tid":52192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Star Wars演員Carrie Fisher心臟病發死咗","createTime":"2016-12-24T00:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T05:02:40.000Z","uid":31888,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd499243519f1bda9155951b149d928d92d73380","tid":52192,"uid":31888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:15:53.000Z","msg":"(TMZ) TMZ is reporting that actress Carrie Fisher suffered a massive heart attack on an airplane.<br />\n<br />\nThey say that she was on a flight from London to LAX when she went into cardiac arrest 15 minutes before the plane landed and an EMT on the plane performed CPR on her. <br />\n<br />\nOnce the plane landed, paramedics performed CPR on Fisher for 15 minutes before they could get a pulse. TMZ says the paramedics rushed the actress to the UCLA Medical Center, according to TMZ. <br />\n<br />\nUSA Today is reporting that the actress is in critical condition. TMZ says she is on a ventilator. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc841ea8d36d7fdf56d269faa054f216276d132","tid":52192,"uid":27362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:18:27.000Z","msg":"死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"ee9b40a5eb8bd3aabb82e92325edab8e41df3d87","tid":52192,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:19:27.000Z","msg":"Learn English"},{"pid":"13a2dd75611b3063387248cfee959509c6de8bf4","tid":52192,"uid":16757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T00:21:47.000Z","msg":"屌 唔撚係啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lom